{"id":299958,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-黑龙江访民张继臣爬上路灯杆撒传单抗议/","date":"2013-06-20T18:03:56Z","modified":"2013-06-20T18:03:56Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江访民张继臣爬上路灯杆撒传单抗议枉法判决（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）黑龙江访民张继臣因控告巴彦县公安局警察姜会臣、刘庆权徇私枉法，检察院、法院枉法判案，长期上访案件得不到解决，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>一大早，爬上了北京公益西桥南面路灯杆顶端，并挂出“张继臣控告黑龙江省巴彦县公安局警察姜会臣刘庆权徇私枉法检察院法院枉法判决”的条幅，还不时地向下撒传单以此抗议司法腐败。直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点</span><span>，人还没下来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今天北京的气温是摄氏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">34</span><span>度，前来解救的消防人员在现场安放救生垫，带有消防云梯车停止旁边。路旁站了很多围观的群众……</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，张继臣的所为是因正常上访不解决问题，走投无路被逼无奈而不得不采取的举措。按照当局一贯的说法：这是过激行为，影响恶劣。但关注张继臣的现场人士不禁质问：这一切又是谁造成的？谁是这起事件的策划者呢？当今社会的不稳定，就是腐败导演出的这一切。希望早一天看到习近平所说的反腐老虎、苍蝇一起打的具体行动，以避免类似事件不要再发生。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5BJEVT2xB48/UcMliV2hb3I/AAAAAAAAjz8/0LS7EYM4WwY/s1600/IMG_1660.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5BJEVT2xB48/UcMliV2hb3I/AAAAAAAAjz8/0LS7EYM4WwY/s320/IMG_1660.jpg\" width=\"238\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ujN1-dQ8Hc0/UcMllW_bTEI/AAAAAAAAj0M/MDlMdcUDxlI/s1600/IMG_1662.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ujN1-dQ8Hc0/UcMllW_bTEI/AAAAAAAAj0M/MDlMdcUDxlI/s320/IMG_1662.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-YU5w1L_OKnI/UcMlj0FXD5I/AAAAAAAAj0A/T7letnyCkfo/s1600/IMG_1670.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-YU5w1L_OKnI/UcMlj0FXD5I/AAAAAAAAj0A/T7letnyCkfo/s320/IMG_1670.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}